reviewText: I liked it.  Watched it a couple times.  Helps inform the problems with a non-literal Genesis interpretation

I thought this DVD was very informative. I have watched it numerous times and have shared it with family and friends. The speaker is a brilliant man with a PhD. in Physics, maybe a little too smart for some.
Too complicated for me to read this. --but I have an excuse. --had an aneurysm 28 years ago.
